#: ../../../contributing/internals.md:3
msgid ""
"Furo's internals contain an interesting mix of stupid-things-that-work and "
"all kinds of bodges. Most of this project was built slowly over the span of "
"a few weeks, as a part of an attempt to take a break from working on Python "
"packaging stuff."
msgstr ""

